Marjorie Bennett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marjorie_Bennett 0 Marjorie Bennett (January 15, 1896 – June 14, 1982) was an Australian-born television and film actress, who worked mainly in Great Britain and the United States. She began her acting career during the silent film era.
